Small cqb map to build up shotgun skills mainly, all players start out with the m3 shotty and a p228. There is a buyzone under the middle light, for those of you that aint into shottys there is a version of the map (fy_underground that has buyzones at both sporns so you can start with your weapon of choice.
any crits or any changes you may need for me to make for your server eg addin more sporn points or anythin like that just gimme a message on messenger clit_the_mapper@hotmail.com ill try sort it for ya.
